snippet.title: Amber Heard welcomes baby girl via surrogate
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has revealed that she has welcomed her first child via surrogate, five years after her nasty split from Johnny Depp. The actress took to Instagram to share a snap of herself cradling her daughter, named Oonagh Paige Heard.
